text: Roswitha Lopez (born 13 November 1969) is a former synchronized swimmer from Aruba. She competed in the women's solo and women's duet at the 1988 Summer Olympics. == References == Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Aruban synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Aruba Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Dutch female swimmers
